OL,13,Fof Al Fayed's apartments after a late
OL,14,Fshift at work.
OL,16,F"I made it obvious that I didn't want
OL,17,Fthat to happen. I did not give
OL,18,Fconsent. I just wanted it to be over,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
